data.title: Leadership Harrisburg Area – Nonprofit Resource Network
data.text:
Leadership Harrisburg Area is a bridge between people, businesses, and the organizations that address the greatest needs of our communities. We are a private, non profit organization established in 1986 with an alumni base of 1200 business and community leaders throughout Pennsylvania’s Capital Region.

Contact Information

3211 North Front Street

Harrisburg, PA 17110

717-216-5200

http://www.leadershipharrisburg.org/

We pride ourselves on maintaining an extensive directory of nonprofit organizations. If you feel that our information is inaccurate, please let us know.
